#test-create(data-role="page")
  div(data-role="header")
    h1= title
  div(data-role="content")
    div(style="float: left; margin: 30px")

      p This is where you can create a Test to be saved and later given.<br/>
      p Everything must be within [&nbsp;]!
        table.border
          tr
            td.border Single Number
            td.border [10]
          tr
            td.border Operators<br/>Generate for all listed
            td.border [+-*/]
          tr
            td.border Specific Numbers
            td.border [1,3,5]
          tr
            td.border Range of Numbers
            td.border [0..9]
      p Let's try it with something easy:
      form#create
        label(for='eq') Equation:
        input(type="text", id='eq', name='eq', value='[10][+-][1,3,5][+][0..9]')
        button(name="generate") Generate Preview
        button(name="create") Create Test

    #preview(style="margin-top: 50px; display: none;")
      table.border
        tr
          td.border Equation:
          td.border#eq
        tr
          td.border Total Possible:
          td.border#total
      p#message
      p Generated Questions:
      table.questions.generate
        tbody.generate
